    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> then score in a criss-cross pattern across the top with a knife</p>",
