    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>chicken,</strong> <strong>leek & carrot pie filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Lay the <strong>puff pastry</strong> sheet over the pie dish and trim off any excess</p><p>Tip: Use any excess pastry to add decorations to the pie!</p><p>Press the edges with a fork to seal the pastry to the dish, then brush all over with <strong>milk</strong></p>",
